<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sum-n">sum <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /sʌm/    美 /sʌm/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>算术：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>do a sum in one’s head 
心算</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[常用单数] 总数；总和；全部：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>The sum of</strong> two and two is four. 
2加2的总和是4。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>That is <strong>the sum of</strong> our experience. 
那就是我们全部的经验。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>金额：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a</strong> large <strong>sum of</strong> money 
一大笔钱</p></div></div>